                <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: C.dim2 }}>수업 {st.auto.count}회 · {st.auto.hours}시간 × {won(st.auto.rate)}{st.extra !== 0 ? ` · 추가 ${st.extra > 0 ? "+" : ""}${won(st.extra)}` : ""}</div>
